summary:
hello! i was tagged by @eversincencwyork to do the “my year in 9 pics” tag
the pictures in order are; my dance team qualifying...
body:
hello! i was tagged by @eversincencwyork to do the “my year in 9 pics” tag

the pictures in order are; my dance team qualifying for state, prom, graduation, pride stl, harry styles concert, interactive introverts, niall horan concert, ed sheeran concert, me and michael clifford from 5sos

2018 was rough, but she was probably my favorite year in a long time. I qualified for state, graduated, saw harry, d&p, niall, ed, taylor swift, 5sos (met ¾) and successfully completed my first semester of college. she was eventful and I cannot wait to see what 2019 holds

not tagging anyone because i don’t have any friends
